{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>現場消息指，今早34歲事主出外上班時，途經啟業邨啟裕樓地下，突然有兩名男子衝來企圖搶走他的袋，期間兩男曾有錘仔扑頭，令事主頭部受傷流血。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260423/1123954593307430912380659.jpeg/NU8m5w7JBMk2lD2NJVpbD-s1xv7Z42n2xDM16uEzNeo\" alt=\"警方到場調查。（黃學潤攝）\"><figcaption>警方到場調查。（黃學潤攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260423/1123954590778134528732401.jpeg/dmlMNgXZxyDn0yoVGrFT2-m8NtJHptzECnvlDy975Q8\" alt=\"事主頭破血流。（黃學潤攝）\"><figcaption>事主頭破血流。（黃學潤攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260423/1123950806111227904589237.jpeg/NhahG9I7ujDafmEtbv795BQsZwDj2EnNnVMgVbhTIFU\" alt=\"警方到場調查。（黃學潤攝）\"><figcaption>警方到場調查。（黃學潤攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260423/1123950802973757440054396.jpeg/xCmcXRxKDnIcSB5Sdkq6uiOOiOQNA5zz_bzvrti8764\" alt=\"現場是啟裕樓。（黃學潤攝）\"><figcaption>現場是啟裕樓。（黃學潤攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260423/1123950796631707648453012.jpeg/HfmHXfRy-y_Ku4EV1GqRWxIbI4mHL0qHSGukkW1rpJE\" alt=\"警方到場調查。（黃學潤攝）\"><figcaption>警方到場調查。（黃學潤攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260423/1123957020853014528748053.jpeg/FJS6FXHYiRloLGlsiWxbjxPFCDy-R105_is9o9srPaM\" alt=\"現場消息指，今早34歲事主出外上班時，途經啟業邨啟裕樓地下，突然有兩名男子衝來企圖搶走他的袋，期間兩男曾有錘仔扑頭，令事主頭部受傷流血。（黃學潤攝）\"><figcaption>現場消息指，今早34歲事主出外上班時，途經啟業邨啟裕樓地下，突然有兩名男子衝來企圖搶走他的袋，期間兩男曾有錘仔扑頭，令事主頭部受傷流血。（黃學潤攝）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-23T04:21:39.605722+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":213,"images":6,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}